article:
This is a list of Australian Commonwealth Government departments, bureaus,
authorities, commissions and corporations.

A new Government led by the Leader of the Australian Labor Party, the Hon
Julia Gillard MP, was sworn in by the Governor-General of Australia on 24 June
2010. The new Government has changed the structure and portfolios of a number
of agencies.
